---
title: Seared Beef Rump & Broccoli Salad with Parmesan & Dijon Mustard
description: Juicy seared beef rump takes centre stage in this fresh and zesty dish! Paired with a crisp broccoli salad, punchy Dijon mustard, and a sprinkle of Parmesan, it’s a perfect balance of bold flavours and bright, cheesy goodness.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

